Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tunakusifu tunakuheshimu twakuabudu tunakutukuza,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Twakushuru kwa ajili yako, ya utukufu wako mkuu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Utukufu juu kwa Mungu,  na amani ulimwenguni, 
(kwa watu  aliowarithia kwa watu aliowarithia)x2</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Mungu Baba ndiwe Mfalme wa mbinguni Baba Mwenyezi,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Yesu Kristu Mwana wa Pekee, mwana kondoo mwana wa Baba.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Utukufu juu kwa Mungu,  na amani ulimwenguni, 
(kwa watu  aliowarithia kwa watu aliowarithia)x2</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uondoaye dhambi za watu, tuhurumie, tusikilize</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tuhurumie mwenye rehema, maombi yetu uyapokee</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Utukufu juu kwa Mungu,  na amani ulimwenguni, 
(kwa watu  aliowarithia kwa watu aliowarithia)x2</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uketiye kuume kwake, Mungu Baba tuhurumie</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa kuwa ndiwe pekee yako, pekee yako Mtakatifu.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Utukufu juu kwa Mungu,  na amani ulimwenguni, 
(kwa watu  aliowarithia kwa watu aliowarithia)x2</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Pamoja naye Roho Mtakatifu, katika utukufu wake. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Anayeishi na kutawala, milele yote Amina.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
