Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai na uiguani guku thi, Kwa andu a wendi mwega ni tugugukumia</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani munene iguru Ngai kihoti,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
