Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani ndurume ya Ngai Mwana wa Ithe,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we uthengagia mehia ma thi tuiguire tha ukumio</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai na uiguani guku thi, Kwa andu a wendi mwega ni tugugukumia</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>We uthengagia mehia ma thi igua ithaitha riitu,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we uikaire urio wa Ithe utuiguire tha ukumio</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai na uiguani guku thi, Kwa andu a wendi mwega ni tugugukumia</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni amu nowe wiki Mutheru Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nowe wiki uri iguru ma Yesu Kristu ukumio</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukumio iguru kwa Ngai na uiguani guku thi, Kwa andu a wendi mwega ni tugugukumia</s></f>"},{ID:21,
