Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngwĩtĩkia nĩ ngwĩtĩkia, nĩ ngwĩtĩkia</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngwĩtĩkia Ngai ũmwe, Ithe Kĩhoti othe, Mũmbi wa igũrũ na thĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wa indo ciothe cionekaga na iria itonekaga na Mwathani o ũmwe </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu Kristũ, Mwana wa Ngai wa mũmwe,
 na mũciare </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ Ithe kuuma mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.Nĩ ngwĩtĩkia  </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngwĩtĩkia nĩ ngwĩtĩkia, nĩ ngwĩtĩkia</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai kuuma kwa Ngai, ũtheri kuuma ũtheri, 
Ngai nginyu kuuma </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai nginyu. Mũciare ũtarĩ mũmbe, wa mũgĩre ũmwe na Ithe; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wombithirie indo ciothe. Na nĩ ũndũ witũ ithuĩ andũ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩguo tũkahonoka akiuma o matuini ni ngwitikia </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngwĩtĩkia nĩ ngwĩtĩkia, nĩ ngwĩtĩkia</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>We nĩ agĩire mwĩrĩ na hinya wa Muoyo Mũtheru he Maria thingi;</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> na agĩtuĩka mũndũ.  Nĩ ambirũo nĩ ũndũ witũ; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Pontio Pilato agĩathana, agĩtandiũrũo na agĩthikwo ni ngwitikia</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngwĩtĩkia nĩ ngwĩtĩkia, nĩ ngwĩtĩkia</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nowe nĩ ariũkire kuri mũthĩ wa ithatũ o mũigana mandĩko ningwitikia </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nĩ ambatire igũrũ aikaraga ũrĩo wa Ithe na ni agacoka ringi ni ngwitikia </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nĩ agacoka rĩngĩ na ũthamaki, gutwira me muoyo na akuo, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>unene wake ndugathira ni ngwitikia </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngwĩtĩkia nĩ ngwĩtĩkia, nĩ ngwĩtĩkia</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngwĩtĩkia Muoyo Mũtheru, Muoyo Mutheru Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uria uheanaga uturo ni ngwitikia :
ũrĩa umaga </s></f>"},{ID:9,
